    <body>When your users attempt to sign in to your applications, they are redirected to a sign-in page hosted by <MadCap:variable name="okta-variables.ProductName" />. You can customize this sign-in page  to provide  a consistent, seamless user experience that fits your brand. The Custom Sign In tab on the Customization page contains a Sign-in Widget and an embedded HTML&#160;editor to help you get started. For detailed information on usage and setup, see the <a href="https://developer.okta.com/docs/guides/custom-hosted-signin/overview/" target="_blank"><a href="https://developer.okta.com/docs/guides/custom-hosted-signin/" target="_blank">Custom Hosted Sign-In Page</a></a> guide.</body>
